# NOTE: 'dist/' was here and it silently excluded ui/dist — our entire interface.
# Once a directory is ignored, git will not let a deeper rule re-include its
# contents, so the ui/.gitignore workaround could not have saved it either.
# We have no generated dist anywhere else, so the rule is simply gone.
# The submission must contain the UI; a build artefact convention must never
# outrank a deliverable.
build/
*.zip
